                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Big bucks for something you may not need.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>3</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>7</span>
